name: Hand Chain Bracelet
description:
I have been asked several times to create a hand chain and finally loved this custom order so much I had to add it to my collection!
A very delicate, but sturdy chain connects the middle finger to the wrist. There is an extender chain for an adjustable fit. 

You can choose from 14K Yellow Gold Filled, 14K Rose Gold Filled, or Sterling Silver.

Gold Filled has 100 times more gold than gold plated jewelry. Gold filled wire is created by taking a sheet of 14 karat gold and bonding it through extreme heat and pressure to a core of semi-precious metal (brass). This is a very sophisticated process and only a few mills in the world do it. You should not mistake this process for gold plating as there is a very big difference.

Gold Filled has 100 times more gold than gold plated jewelry. Gold filled wire is created by taking a sheet of 14 karat gold and bonding it through extreme heat and pressure to a core of semi-precious metal (brass). This is a very sophisticated process and only a few mills in the world do it. You should not mistake this process for gold plating as there is a very big difference.


AVAILABLE IN SIZES 1-11
 I find the top knuckle rings to be about 3 sizes smaller than the regular ring size for the finger.

Choose from 14K Gold Filled, 14K Pink Gold Filled, or Sterling Silver. 

These are hand forged, lightly hammered, soldered from sturdy 14 gauge wire, and are made to order.


Gold Filled has 100 times more gold than gold plated jewelry. Gold filled wire is created by taking a sheet of 14 karat gold and bonding it through extreme heat and pressure to a core of semi-precious metal (brass). This is a very sophisticated process and only a few mills in the world do it. You should not mistake this process for gold plating as there is a very big difference.
